{"tid":109913,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手入門]風景相片的計劃","createTime":"2017-02-06T10:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T11:33:13.000Z","uid":12599,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99897e2fffea261943ab89c3a7851c5ec3a8f2c6","tid":109913,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"要影一張好的風景相,事前的計劃是非常重要的。現今科技先進,大家可以輕鬆取得各種資訊,特別是在香港,不論想登高拍攝,還是拍攝城市景色,事前計劃的資訊可謂手到拿來。今日就介紹一下筆者自己的風景攝影計劃,讓攝影新手作一個參考。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 天氣</strong><br />\n<br />\n天氣對於攝影有決定性的影響。一般來說香港的夏天時的高氣壓會帶來晴朗的天氣,亦會同時帶來高溫。由於地理原因,香港冬季多吹北風,而中國的空氣污染是出了名的嚴重,轉吹北風時多會為香港帶來毒霧污染。春季也是香港拍攝雲海的最佳時機,但筆者對此並不熟悉,之後有機會再探討一下這方面的拍攝計劃。一般而言,香港5月到9月都是拍攝大景的好時機。<br />\n<br />\n香港位置非常接近北回歸線,想要拍出像外國的極藍天色,是很困難的。但香港在天朗氣清的日子,能見度是足夠由大帽山望到澳門。可惜這樣的日子不多,有機會的話就盡可能出動。<br />\n<br />\n查詢天氣有兩個非常有用的網址:<br />\na. 香港天文台: <a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcontentc.htm&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e5e9df55\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm</a><br />\nb. Google Weather (在Google Search打入地點+天氣就有):<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BlcDUs4b_p8/WGMqgUD7GnI/AAAAAAAAe_g/ouo9qlPyrxMHfauoQNCmmDzwbcKqBxoBACLcB/s400/%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-BlcDUs4b_p8%2FWGMqgUD7GnI%2FAAAAAAAAe_g%2Fouo9qlPyrxMHfauoQNCmmDzwbcKqBxoBACLcB%2Fs400%2F%2525E4%2525B8%25258B%2525E8%2525BC%252589.png&h=e29d0157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩者而言我比較推薦Google的天氣預報系統,不單較為準確,而且有降雨機率預測,界面亦比較整潔。<br />\n<br />\n除當日的陰晴分布外,溫度及潮汐都是要留意的地方。高溫及寒冷的天氣均需帶備合適的衣物及食水,特別是前往郊外地區,萬全的準備是必要的。另外如需到海邊的地方拍攝,潮汐漲退也會有影響。<br />\n<br />\n對於雲海及天文拍攝,天氣的影響更加大了,由於此類攝影所需的氣象準備較多,暫且不談。"},{"pid":"eaa4a227a68508dae85d1ec69d59df244fa4bfa4","tid":109913,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>2. 地點的選擇</strong><br />\n<br />\n決定拍攝的地點,有兩個最重要的因素: a. 太陽方位 及 b. 風景<br />\n決定太陽的方位,筆者有幾個推介:<br />\nSunCalc (Desktop 用): <a href=\"http://suncalc.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuncalc.net%2F&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=00f529ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://suncalc.net/</a><br />\nExsate Golden Hour (Android): <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=exsate.goldenhour&amp;hl=zh_TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dexsate.goldenhour%26hl%3Dzh_TW&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4e85eefd\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=exsate.goldenhour&amp;hl=zh_TW</a><br />\nGolden Hour (IOS): <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/golden-hour/id362345691?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fgolden-hour%2Fid362345691%3Fmt%3D8&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f531776e\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/golden-hour/id362345691?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n由於地軸傾斜的關係,日出日落的地點每日都有不同,事前計算太陽方位是非常重要的。以下用SunCalc作為例子:<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wuX9b28QFp8/WGMt1bpdmXI/AAAAAAAAe_s/WAKZjtNJBzY6AXPE7Msxy3ZO13xHrShwwCLcB/s640/%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%2B%25281%2529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-wuX9b28QFp8%2FWGMt1bpdmXI%2FAAAAAAAAe_s%2FWAKZjtNJBzY6AXPE7Msxy3ZO13xHrShwwCLcB%2Fs640%2F%2525E4%2525B8%25258B%2525E8%2525BC%252589%252B%2525281%252529.png&h=52c1cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ni. 在上方輸入地點與拍攝日期<br />\nii. 上方的時間軸及地圖右上方會顯示出該時該地的日出日落時間及Magic Hour長度,這是非常重要的參考指標<br />\niii. 地圖上會顯示出太陽的行走路徑。由於輸入時間為冬天,因此日出日落位置會偏南。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提,春分及秋分為太陽正東升起的日子,而夏至及冬至則為太陽方位最北及最南的日子。夏至時日照時間最長,冬至時日照最短,春分及秋分則日夜半分。<br />\n<br />\nMagic Hour則是指太陽在降下/升出水平線前的半小時。在天文的角度,日出及日落在時間上是相反的,因此單從相片很難分辨出究竟是日出還是日落。不過日出的大氣較為穩定,夜間在市區的空氣污染亦較少,所以日出照的大氣通透度一般會比較高。但日出的代價是要早起床,對於夜訓的香港人而且,日落的時間及交通是比較方便的。<br />\n<br />\n在選擇地點方面,大家可以善用Google Map的立體及街景功能,配合SunCalc可說是風景攝影的兩大利器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sRjlOnATz_o/WGMxeaOHTDI/AAAAAAAAe_8/Kp_8BKGvJjwx9jUEmpvd_SFktiP_YNsxACLcB/s1600/%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%2B%25282%2529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-sRjlOnATz_o%2FWGMxeaOHTDI%2FAAAAAAAAe_8%2FKp_8BKGvJjwx9jUEmpvd_SFktiP_YNsxACLcB%2Fs1600%2F%2525E4%2525B8%25258B%2525E8%2525BC%252589%252B%2525282%252529.png&h=4fbaaa9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle Map要轉成3D模式,要先在左下角按衛星模式,再接Ctrl + Mouse左鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-mGfKhSDQpRs/WGMxeQhrUII/AAAAAAAAe_4/DX0Qj4GUhu0BJ-HlbS3vE8koU4f7msk7gCLcB/s640/%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%2B%25283%2529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-mGfKhSDQpRs%2FWGMxeQhrUII%2FAAAAAAAAe_4%2FDX0Qj4GUhu0BJ-HlbS3vE8koU4f7msk7gCLcB%2Fs640%2F%2525E4%2525B8%25258B%2525E8%2525BC%252589%252B%2525283%252529.png&h=9925f150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n移到打算拍攝地的位置,調整接近水平的角度及SunCalc計算出的日出日落方位。圖中為香港著名日落地點海運大廈天台。<br />\n<br />\n利用Google Map的3D模式,大家可以發現到香港其實有不少隱世攝影秘點...至於那裡有好地方,就要由大家慢慢去發掘了。"},{"pid":"8d7172a1e674ba4d09b84a01efadf09f3e066a64","tid":109913,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>3. 日出日落拍攝</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港的交通是非常的方便,如果大家想拍攝日出日落,筆者建議在日出日落時間最少半小時前抵達拍攝地點。抵達後可先在附近走一個圈,找出較佳的拍攝角度。然後就落三腳架及調整相機拍攝參數。攝影技巧就不談了,但以日落拍攝而言,日落後半小時的Magic Hour天地反差會減少。如拍攝城市景色,在日落後半小時會燈光漸亮,此時是拍攝城市景色的最佳時間。<br />\n<br />\n最後想說的是,如果大家想拍攝上飽和度較高的藍天,選擇日出後兩小時內拍攝是最佳的時間。由於藍天的成因的太陽光的散射,在日出後的時間太陽與地面夾角較小,順光(太陽在背後)時藍色光散色最為強烈,因為天空在此時最漂亮。加上由於太陽光是側光,相對於正午的頂光,相片的立體感會較強烈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8567/27901505554_fec31a432b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8567%2F27901505554_fec31a432b_b.jpg&h=86908f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太陽仍在水平線上,稱為Golden Hour的時間,天地反差仍然很高,但此類光適合順光人像拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8219/28492069125_3c3b0bcf1e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8219%2F28492069125_3c3b0bcf1e_b.jpg&h=c3ea79da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMagic Hour 時加上天朗氣清的日子,會出現反曙光現像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7120/27185341733_eb1df53bd2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7120%2F27185341733_eb1df53bd2_b.jpg&h=3c10cdbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍攝城市的景氣,日落後半小時華燈初上是最佳時機。<br />\n<br />\n雖然上文有很大部分都是介紹日出日落景,不過其技巧可以應用到其他風景相上。新手的風景相入門就到說到這裡,其他的攝影技巧,有機會再說吧。<br />\n<br />\n文章同步發佈於Blogger及Photoblog:<br />\nBlogger: <a href=\"http://optikahk.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foptikahk.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F02%2Fblog-post.html&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=72141774\" target=\"_blank\">http://optikahk.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\nPhotoblog: <a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/181527/%EF%BC%BB%E8%AE%80%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E7%A8%BF%EF%BC%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%99%AF%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2F181527%2F%25EF%25BC%25BB%25E8%25AE%2580%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A8%25BF%25EF%25BC%25BD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3ac20c1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/181527/%EF%BC%BB%E8%AE%80%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E7%A8%BF%EF%BC%BD%E9%A2%A8%E6%99%AF%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83</a>"},{"pid":"cb05bbbc90e6c76393f8ea82cc61a3211503c833","tid":109913,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"476a72177dab64093288993316738596ce178d75","tid":109913,"uid":1952,"like":0,"dislike":0,